---
title: Rosemary Crusted Meatloaf with Squash Mash
description: Rosemary and mustard crusted hamburger steaks give you all the Sunday roast feelings without all the work. Squash mash and garlicky green beans balance out this tasty plate, and we all know Sunday dinner isn't complete without gravy!

